sequenceDiagram
    participant OS as 操作系统
    participant App as Spring Boot 应用
    participant GS as WebServerGracefulShutdownLifecycle
    participant WS as WebServer
    participant Conn as Connector
    participant Req as 在途请求

    Note over App: server.shutdown=graceful<br/>spring.lifecycle.timeout-per-shutdown-phase=30s

    OS->>App: SIGTERM
    App->>App: 关闭钩子触发
    App->>GS: stop()

    GS->>WS: shutDownGracefully(callback)
    Note right of WS: 1. 停止接收新连接
    WS->>Conn: pause()
    Conn-->>WS: 监听暂停

    Note over GS,Req: 2. 等待在途请求完成
    loop 最多等 30s
        GS->>WS: check()
        WS-->>GS: 还有 N 个在途请求
    end

    GS->>WS: 强制关闭 (timeout)
    WS->>Conn: stop()
    Conn-->>WS: 端口释放

    GS->>App: callback.onShutdown()
    App->>App: 关闭 ApplicationContext
    App-->>OS: 进程退出 (exit 0)
